      <h2>Problem Statement</h2>
      <p>Writers often struggle to structure their story ideas into coherent outlines, especially when working with vague or underdeveloped concepts. They need a tool that can take a simple idea and turn it into a detailed, organized story structure.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Our Solution</h2>
      <p>Using prompt engineering, Story Smith converts vague user inputs into detailed, structured prompts that guide an AI model — like GPT-4 — to generate comprehensive story outlines. This makes it easy for writers to develop full narratives from just a seed of an idea.</p>
